title: Boykin helps No. 2 TCU rally past Kansas State, 52-45

TCU quarterback Trevone Boykin (2) passes to a teammate during the first half of an NCAA college football game against Kansas State in Manhattan, Kan., Saturday, Oct. 10, 2015. (AP Photo/Orlin Wagner)   
Kansas State quarterback Joe Hubener (8) points out the defense to offensive lineman Dalton Risner, left, during the first half of an NCAA college football game against TCU in Manhattan, Kan., Saturday, Oct. 10, 2015. (AP Photo/Orlin Wagner)   
Kansas State head coach Bill Snyder, center, stands with his team during the first half of an NCAA college football game against TCU in Manhattan, Kan., Saturday, Oct. 10, 2015. (AP Photo/Orlin Wagner)   
TCU safety Nick Orr (18) breaks up a pass to Kansas State wide receiver Deante Burton, back, during the first half of an NCAA college football game in Manhattan, Kan., Saturday, Oct. 10, 2015. (AP Photo/Orlin Wagner)   
TCU head coach Gary Patterson talks with players during the first half of an NCAA college football game against Kansas State in Manhattan, Kan., Saturday, Oct. 10, 2015. (AP Photo/Orlin Wagner)   
TCU running back Aaron Green (22) breaks loose on a touchdown run during the first half of an NCAA college football game against Kansas State in Manhattan, Kan., Saturday, Oct. 10, 2015. (AP Photo/Orlin Wagner)   
Kansas State kick-return specialist Dalvin Warmack (3) is tackled by TCU special teams player Alec Dunham during the first half of an NCAA college football game in Manhattan, Kan., Saturday, Oct. 10, 2015.
